---
title: Indo Chinese Style Chilli Tofu with Stir-Fried Veg and Basmati Rice
description: Our Indo Chinese Style Chilli Tofu is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R43_W34_UK_G10119-15596-3_Main_3_high-2d29f4a5.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/6491c3bf0635a1e9befbb5dc.pdf
